<SYNC Start=4376120><P Class=KRCC>
"알라만이 참 신입니다"
<SYNC Start=4380745><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4381034><P Class=KRCC>
말해!
<SYNC Start=4382838><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4382955><P Class=KRCC>
